<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Morning Letter for Alya</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@600&family=Poppins:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #ffe4e1;
            --accent-pink: #ffb6c1;
            --text-color: #5d4037;
        }

        body, html {
            margin: 0; padding: 0; height: 100%;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .screen {
            display: none; height: 100vh; width: 100%;
            flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
            align-items: center; text-align: center;
            position: absolute;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5f6 0%, #ffe4e1 100%);
        }

        .active { display: flex; }

        .content-box {
            position: relative; z-index: 10;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 2.5px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.4);
            max-width: 85%;
        }

        .oi-pendek { font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 5px; opacity: 0.8; font-weight: bold; }
        .moon-pie { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; display: block; }
        
        h1 { font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 2.8rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #ff69b4; margin-top: 0; }
        
        button {
            padding: 14px 45px; font-size: 1.1rem;
            background-color: var(--accent-pink); color: white;
            border: none; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 25px; transition: 0.4s;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 182, 193, 0.6);
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        button:hover { background-color: #ff8fa3; transform: scale(1.05); }

        .password-container { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin: 25px 0; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .pass-input {
            width: 35px; height: 45px; text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.3rem; border: 2px solid var(--accent-pink);
            border-radius: 10px; background: white; outline: none;
        }

        #screen4 { overflow-y: auto; display: none; }
        #screen4.active { display: block; height: 100vh; }
        .letter-container { padding: 80px 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
        .letter-text { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; max-width: 600px; white-space: pre-wrap; }
        
        .floating-flower { position: absolute; font-size: 2rem; opacity: 0.4; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="screen1" class="screen active">
        <span class="floating-flower" style="top: 10%; left: 15%;">🌸</span>
        <span class="floating-flower" style="bottom: 10%; right: 15%;">🌺</span>
        <div class="content-box">
            <p class="oi-pendek">oi pendek :p</p>
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 5px;">🎀 🌸 🎀</div>
            <span class="moon-pie">🌙 🥧</span>
            <h1>Morning Letter for Alya</h1>
            <button onclick="nextScreen(1, 2)">Enter</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="screen2" class="screen">
        <span class="floating-flower" style="top: 20%; right: 10%;">🌷</span>
        <div class="content-box">
            <h1>Helloo Babyy...</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 20px 0;">kamuu kasi password dulu baru sia kasi :p</p>
            <button onclick="nextScreen(2, 3)">Okay!</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="screen3" class="screen">
        <div class="content-box">
            <p style="font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Masukkan 8 digit password:</p>
            <div class="password-container" id="otp-inputs"></div>
            <p id="error-msg" style="color: #ff4d6d; display: none; font-size: 0.9rem;">Password salah, cuba lagi!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="screen4" class="screen">
        <div class="letter-container">
            <div class="content-box">
                <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px;">🎀 🌸 🎀</div>
                <div class="letter-text">
Good morning, my love! I hope you woke up feeling refreshed and ready to take on the day with that beautiful smile of yours. I wanted to start your morning with a little reminder of how much you mean to me and how grateful I am to have you in my life. First and foremost, please don't forget to have your breakfast. I know how busy things can get, but you need that energy to keep you going, so please eat something delicious and filling for me.

Your health and well-being are so important to me, so please take care of yourself throughout the day. Don't push yourself too hard and remember to take breaks when you need them. I want you to stay strong and happy, always. 

Looking back, it’s amazing to think about our journey together. My love for you has only grown deeper since June 2024, and every moment since then has been a treasure. From the day we started this journey until this very second, you have been my greatest joy. I want you to know that no matter what happens, through the highs and the lows, I am always going to be right here by your side. You never have to face anything alone because I’ve got your back, today and every day that follows.

You are my rock, my peace, and my favorite person to talk to. I hope your day is as wonderful and bright as you are. Go out there and shine, but remember that I’m always just a message away if you need anything at all. I love you more than words can say, from 2024 until forever. Have a beautiful day, sweetheart! ❤️
                </div>
                <div style="font-size: 3rem; color: #ff4d6d; margin-top: 30px; animation: heartbeat 1.5s infinite; display: inline-block;">💖</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function nextScreen(current, next) {
            document.getElementById('screen' + current).classList.remove('active');
            document.getElementById('screen' + next).classList.add('active');
        }

        const otpContainer = document.getElementById('otp-inputs');
        const correctPass = "13092012";
        let inputs = [];

        for (let i = 0; i < 8; i++) {
            let input = document.createElement('input');
            input.type = 'text'; input.maxLength = 1; input.className = 'pass-input';
            input.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
                if (e.target.value && i < 7) inputs[i+1].focus();
                checkPassword();
            });
            input.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
                if (e.key === "Backspace" && !e.target.value && i > 0) {
                    inputs[i-1].focus();
                }
            });
            otpContainer.appendChild(input);
            inputs.push(input);
        }

        function checkPassword() {
            let val = inputs.map(i => i.value).join('');
            if (val.length === 8) {
                if (val === correctPass) {
                    nextScreen(3, 4);
                } else {
                    document.getElementById('error-msg').style.display = 'block';
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        inputs.forEach(i => i.value = '');
                        inputs[0].focus();
                        document.getElementById('error-msg').style.display = 'none';
                    }, 800);
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
